185259.name: Human Male HYDRATH Uniform
185259.tooltip: "You must be the evil you want to see in the world."

185262.name: Human Male Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185262.tooltip: "We are born selfish and greedy...and then society forces us to pretend otherwise."

185265.name: Human Female HYDRATH Uniform
185265.tooltip: "The purpose of life is to beat everyone else. And if you can't beat them, don't help them."

185268.name: Human Female Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185268.tooltip: "Superiority is not something ready-made. It comes from your own conquests."

185271.name: High Elf Male HYDRATH Uniform
185271.tooltip: "Be cruel whenever it's an option. It is always an option."

185274.name: High Elf Male Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185274.tooltip: "We can never achieve evil in the outer world until we foster evil within ourselves."

185277.name: High Elf Female HYDRATH Uniform
185277.tooltip: "You have to believe in yourself, even when you hate everyone else."

185280.name: High Elf Female Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185280.tooltip: "If you love people, you'll have no time to judge them."

185283.name: Amani Male HYDRATH Uniform
185283.tooltip: "One of the greatest strengths is to be everything to someone."

185286.name: Amani Male Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185286.tooltip: "First they fear you, then they fight you, then they bow to you, and then you win."

185289.name: Amani Female HYDRATH Uniform
185289.tooltip: "Where peace is our master, there is no possibility of real victory."

185292.name: Amani Female Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185292.tooltip: "If you set out to be feared, you should be prepared to never compromise, so that you can achieve everything."

185295.name: Castanic Male HYDRATH Uniform
185295.tooltip: "The best things in life are free: hunger, yearning, desire, rage, arrogance, torpor, hate."

185298.name: Castanic Male Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185298.tooltip: "An eye for an eye makes the world see things your way."

185301.name: Castanic Female HYDRATH Uniform
185301.tooltip: "Fear has its use, but cowardice has none."

185304.name: Castanic Female Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185304.tooltip: "Leadership at one time meant compromise; but today it means power."

185307.name: Popori HYDRATH Uniform
185307.tooltip: "When strength supplants restraint and courtesy, one becomes irresistible."

185310.name: Popori Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185310.tooltip: "Suffering is the best form of violence."

185313.name: Elin HYDRATH Uniform
185313.tooltip: "The spirit of envy can never build, but it can destroy."

185316.name: Elin Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185316.tooltip: "In a gentle way, you can destroy the world."

185319.name: Baraka HYDRATH Uniform
185319.tooltip: "If you can't feed a hundred people, watch them starve."

185322.name: Baraka Dyeable HYDRATH Uniform
185322.tooltip: "Morality is contraband in the pursuit of power."

185325.name: HYDRATH-Blue Coat
185325.tooltip: In the hierarchy of the secret organization, HYDRATH-Blue agents are tasked with spreading misery.

185328.name: HYDRATH-Black Coat
185328.tooltip: In the hierarchy of the secret organization, HYDRATH-Black agents are tasked with instilling fear.

185331.name: HYDRATH-Red Coat
185331.tooltip: In the hierarchy of the secret organization, HYDRATH-Red agents are tasked with unleashing rage.

185334.name: HYDRATH-Blue Cap
185334.tooltip: Among HYDRATH-Blue agents, the cap represents experience and authority.

185337.name: HYDRATH-Black Cap
185337.tooltip: Among HYDRATH-Black agents, the cap represents intimidation and superiority.

185340.name: HYDRATH-Red Beret
185340.tooltip: HYDRATH-Red's elite strike team wear these berets to mark them as the organization's most unpredictable rage-monsters.

185343.name: HYDRATH-Black Beret
185343.tooltip: HYDRATH-Black's Terror Commissars wear these berets to mark them as the organization's most tyrannical officers.

185346.tooltip: Strut your stuff in Hello Kitty style!

185349.tooltip: Stand out from the crowd in high Hello Kitty fashion!

185352.tooltip: No matter the school, the cool cats and kittens wear their Hello Kitty gear with pride!

185355.name: Hello Kitty Human Female Black Uniform

185763.name: Human Male Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185763.tooltip: "You have to work on the nut behind the wheel before you start fixing bolts in the engine."

185766.name: Human Male Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185766.tooltip: "Straight roads are for fast cars. Turns are for fast drivers."

185769.name: Human Female Go-Kart Guy Costume
185769.tooltip: "Try to wear out your rear tires before you wear out your front tires."

185772.name: Human Female Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185772.tooltip: A racing uniform that lets them know you intend to finish first.

185775.name: Human Female Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185775.tooltip: "Demure on her feet. Bold in the driver's seat!"

185778.name: High Elf Male Go-Kart Guy Costume
185778.tooltip: "There is no terrible way to win. There is only winning."

185781.name: High Elf Male Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185781.tooltip: "The harder you work, the luckier you become."

185784.name: High Elf Male Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185784.tooltip: "No one remembers who finished second...except the one who finished second."

185787.name: High Elf Female Go-Kart Guy Costume
185787.tooltip: "Once you've raced, you never forget it...and you never get over it."

185790.name: High Elf Female Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185790.tooltip: The uniform that lets everyone know that racing is in your blood.

185793.name: High Elf Female Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185793.tooltip: "You always remember the near-misses. Everyone else remembers the crashes."

185796.name: Amani Male Go-Kart Guy Costume
185796.tooltip: "Winners win races...but champions make it look like it was easy."

185799.name: Amani Male Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185799.tooltip: Passing an aman on the track is like trying to take a bone out of a naga's teeth.

185802.name: Amani Male Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185802.tooltip: A uniform for anyone who lives life a quarter-mile at a time.

185805.name: Amani Female Go-Kart Guy Costume
185805.tooltip: The uniform for when you feel the need for speed.

185808.name: Amani Female Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185808.tooltip: "The trick is not to run out of talent halfway around a corner."

185811.name: Amani Female Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185811.tooltip: "Just put the pedal to the metal until fear transforms into joy."

185814.name: Castanic Male Go-Kart Guy Costume
185814.tooltip: "If everything seems under control, you're not going fast enough."

185817.name: Castanic Male Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185817.tooltip: "It's not when you brake that counts, but when you take them off."

185820.name: Castanic Male Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185820.tooltip: "Second place is just the first-place loser."

185823.name: Castanic Female Go-Kart Guy Costume
185823.tooltip: "A Go-Kart racer needs to be fed a diet of other Go-Kart racers."

185826.name: Castanic Female Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185826.tooltip: "Racing is the essence of life. Everything that comes before or after is just waiting."

185829.name: Castanic Female Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185829.tooltip: A racing uniform that looks best from behind...because that's all they should ever see, anyway.

185832.name: Popori Go-Kart Guy Costume
185832.tooltip: Wear the racing uniform that brings out your inner beast.

185835.name: Popori Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185835.tooltip: "When you run out of tricks, that's when you get lapped."

185838.name: Popori Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185838.tooltip: "It's all about attitude. If you think you're a Go-Kart racer, then, well, you're a Go-Kart racer."

185841.name: Elin Go-Kart Guy Costume
185841.tooltip: "You have to have the right blend of aggression and patience."

185844.name: Elin Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185844.tooltip: "There's no such thing as a bad win...or a good loss."

185847.name: Elin Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185847.tooltip: "Only half the race is about beating the other racers. The other half is about beating the track."

185850.name: Baraka Go-Kart Guy Costume
185850.tooltip: "Racing used to be about wide drivers and skinny tires. Now it is the other way around."

185853.name: Baraka Go-Kart Buzz Costume
185853.tooltip: "Every time I go out there, I am racing with Death. I have yet to come in second."

185856.name: Baraka Go-Kart Daisy Costume
185856.tooltip: Just the thing to wear in the winner's circle!

185862.name: Go-Kart Buzz Mask
185862.tooltip: At these speeds, it's important to have your head on straight.

185865.name: Go-Kart Daisy Mask
185865.tooltip: Let 'em know you're going places...even if it's just the finish line.

185951.name: Butterfly Shuriken
185951.tooltip: So cute, but so deadly...just like the ninja who wields it.

185953.name: Kunoichi Robe
185953.tooltip: A ninja's elegant robe, for formal occasions...or assassinations.

186495.name: Castanic Female Sweet Beats Outfit

186498.name: Dyeable Castanic Female Sweet Beats Outfit

186504.name: Dyeable Popori Def Jams Outfit

186507.name: Elin Sweet Beats Outfit

186510.name: Dyeable Elin Sweet Beats Outfit
